cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper deals with explaining neural network decisions, which is a common topic in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) is also mentioned in the abstract, indicating that these sub-categories are relevant. Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation of explanation methods, which could fall under the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR) if the evaluation involves assessing the security of the neural network.
